{
  "stem": "628.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The boy from Holland who wrote the book, he went on a search, and he-- because they said that he was-- that they met in Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had a gathering and they were talking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What happened to that little-- that [NON-ENGLISH], Helmust Szprycer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Next day when I telephone them, I told them that I'm-- yes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We talked about you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sherry Dons made the film.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I said, where are they?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She gave me the telephone number from the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I telephoned them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Helmut, is that you?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I'll-- so sudden-- Los Angeles, and [NON-ENGLISH], I telephoned.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He went mad.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I went mad.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After three weeks I said, I come over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He came over.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So suddenly, there was that first experience, that we-- the group from the camp got together.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's America.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That book existed, which I've got here-- that day, what I told you about Bloch, going to the German consul.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "These two journalist went with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I gave them the book.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Bloch had to-- on the way to Brussels, they had the story.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Suddenly they saw this was more interesting, the story, then from the German ambasade, from the--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we went in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said to the-- the first thing I said to the German is, is it going to start again?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In German, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, what do you mean?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, don't tell me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Don't tell me, I said in German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is not-- this is the-- what's it called?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Turks or the other peoples, the Algerians.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But indirectly, you're doing it to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said it to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Will it happen again?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I said, how do you-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I said, tell me something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Do you teach in Germany in your school about the Holocaust?",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
